  path="/about" current="/about" palette="0.20"
  jsonLd={lds.length>=1 ? lds[0] : null}
  rail={[{"id": "ch-00", "num": "00", "label": "Opening"}, {"id": "ch-01", "num": "01", "label": "Practice"}, {"id": "ch-02", "num": "02", "label": "Brand"}, {"id": "ch-03", "num": "03", "label": "Begin"}]}
>
  <link slot="head" rel="stylesheet" href="/brand/brand-core.css">


  <section class="chapter" id="ch-00" data-chapter="0" data-palette="0.10">
    <div class="inner" style="text-align:center; align-items:center;">
      <div class="ch-head fade-up" style="justify-content:center;">
        <span class="hashmark"><i></i></span>
        <div class="meta" style="border:0; padding:0;">
          <span class="eyebrow">About &middot; Patrick Milhaupt</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h1 class="headline" data-headline="">
        An advisor's <em>practice</em>.
      </h1>
      <p class="body fade-up" style="margin: 0 auto; text-align:center;">
        More than fifteen years across real-estate investment, asset management, and luxury brokerage. One advisor, one calendar &mdash; and a market read that starts <strong>fresh every morning</strong>.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row fade-up" style="justify-content:center;">
        <a class="btn" href="#ch-01">Continue &darr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="chapter" id="ch-01" data-chapter="1" data-palette="0.30">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="ch-head fade-up">
        <span class="num">01</span>
        <div class="meta">
          <span class="eyebrow">Chapter One</span>
          <span class="sub">The Practice</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="headline" data-headline="">
        Tailored service.<br>Institutional <em>discipline</em>.
      </h2>
      <p class="body fade-up">
        Patrick came to brokerage from the institutional side of real estate. After a BA from Notre Dame and an MS in Real Estate from the University of San Diego, he spent nine years in acquisitions and asset management &mdash; AvalonBay Communities, Alliant Capital, World Class Holdings, and HG Capital &mdash; underwriting more than $500 million in institutional portfolios before joining Sotheby's International Realty in 2016.
      </p>
      <p class="body fade-up">
        That training shapes the practice. Every listing call opens with a market dashboard pulled from the MLS that morning; every pricing recommendation is reconciled across three independent valuation methods before it goes to market. One advisor, one calendar &mdash; backed by a daily-reconciled market database and the Sotheby's pre-market network. In 2024 the practice closed $13.1 million in volume at an average price of $2.02 million, earning RealTrends Verified Top Agent recognition.
      </p>
      <div class="kpi-grid">
        <div class="kpi"><span class="l">National Standing</span><span class="v" style="font-size:22px;">Top 2%</span><span class="d up">RealTrends Verified Top Agent &middot; 2024</span></div>
        <div class="kpi pop"><span class="l">Villages Covered</span><span class="v">7</span><span class="d up">Lake Forest &middot; Winnetka &middot; Kenilworth &middot; Glencoe &middot; Wilmette &middot; Highland Park &middot; Lake Bluff</span></div>
        <div class="kpi"><span class="l">Institutional Career</span><span class="v" style="font-size:22px;">$500M</span><span class="d up">Underwritten before brokerage</span></div>
        <div class="kpi"><span class="l">Years in the Business</span><span class="v" style="font-size:22px;">15+</span><span class="d up">Investment &middot; asset mgmt &middot; brokerage</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="chapter" id="ch-02" data-chapter="2" data-palette="0.60">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="ch-head fade-up">
        <span class="num">02</span>
        <div class="meta">
          <span class="eyebrow">Chapter Two</span>
          <span class="sub">Jameson Sotheby's International Realty</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="headline" data-headline="">
        The brand.<br>The <em>corridor</em>.
      </h2>
      <p class="body fade-up">
        Jameson Sotheby's International Realty is the Chicago affiliate of the Sotheby's International Realty global network &mdash; founded in 1976 inside the venerable auction house (est. 1744), today connecting <strong>1,100+ offices across 86 countries and territories</strong> with the most-recognized brand in luxury real estate. For represented homes, the marketing footprint runs from a private pre-launch through global syndication into the Wall Street Journal Mansion section, the New York Times, the Financial Times, Architectural Digest, Mansion Global, Bloomberg, RESIDE&reg; Magazine, the Houseguest video series, and the only real-estate app on Apple TV. For discerning buyers, the same network is a gateway to homes that are never publicly advertised &mdash; a quiet, curated pipeline measured in days, not weeks.
      </p>
      <p class="body fade-up">
        The Sotheby's editorial work has been cited on this practice. <em>Crain's Chicago Business</em> and <em>The Real Deal</em> have covered the listings, including the 999 Lake Road episode (the on-the-record source on the Caleb Williams story) and the Harris estate at 2441 Woodbridge Lane. The brand opens the door; the practice does the work.
      </p>
      <div class="kpi-grid">
        <div class="kpi"><span class="l">Network</span><span class="v" style="font-size:22px;">1,100+ offices</span><span class="d">Across 86 countries &amp; territories</span></div>
        <div class="kpi pop"><span class="l">2025 Global Volume</span><span class="v" style="font-size:22px;">$182.4B</span><span class="d up">+9.3% YoY in the U.S.</span></div>
        <div class="kpi"><span class="l">Brokerage</span><span class="v" style="font-size:22px;">Jameson SIR</span><span class="d">Chicago affiliate &middot; Lake Forest &amp; Winnetka offices</span></div>
        <div class="kpi"><span class="l">Illinois License</span><span class="v" style="font-size:22px;">#475.177332</span><span class="d">Active Member &middot; Fitzgerald Institute, Notre Dame</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- Press & proof (v11.2 — verified citations only) -->
