          <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-3,#8896AD);margin-top:8px;">Crain's Chicago Business &middot; April 2025</div>
        </div>
        <div style="border-left:1px solid rgba(197,165,114,.4);padding-left:20px;">
          <div style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:19px;color:var(--ink-1,#F0E6D2);line-height:1.5;">&ldquo;We've got a lot of Bears players, several of which are my clients.&rdquo;</div>
          <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-3,#8896AD);margin-top:8px;">Patrick Milhaupt, quoted in <a href="https://therealdeal.com/people/patrick-milhaupt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:inherit;">The Real Deal</a> &middot; September 2024</div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--ink-3,#8896AD);margin-top:10px;">
          Top 2% of Realtors nationally &middot; basis: RealTrends Verified, 2024 production ($13.1M volume &middot; 6.5 sides &middot; $2.02M average price).
        </p>
