      <h2 class="headline" data-headline="">
        A <em>conversation</em>.
      </h2>
      <p class="body fade-up" style="margin: 0 auto; text-align:center;">
        Thirty minutes. No pitch. A direct conversation about what you're trying to do &mdash; and an honest read on whether I'm the right advisor to help you do it. If I'm not, I know who is.
      </p>
